D (conference)|TED]] video, July 2010. [http://initforthegold.blogspot.com/2010/09/rockstrom-on-planetary-boundaries.html Transcript html]\n* {{Twitter|jrockstrom}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rockstrom, Johan}}\n[[Category:Swedish hydrologists]]\n[[Category:Sustainability advocates]]\n[[Category:Stockholm University faculty]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1965 births]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toDaimler(link changed toDaimler AG; link changed toDaimler AG) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johan_Rockstr%C3%B6m"}
